  "title": "carpenter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will work independently to measure, cut, shape, fit, and install wooden building materials during construction, maintenance, and repair of structures such as homes and furniture.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Measure timber accurately to prepare for cutting and fitting</li><li>Cut and shape wood materials to specified dimensions for construction and repair tasks</li><li>Install wooden components securely in homes, furniture, and other structures</li><li>Fit and finish timber surfaces to meet quality and safety standards</li><li>Work independently with minimal supervision to complete carpentry tasks efficiently</li></ul>",
